high_descs: turn to your left, head toward the sink, then turn right and head to the bathtub
pick up the pink bar of soap from the edge of the tub
turn around and head to the cabinet and sink across the room
put the soap in the sink, rinse the soap, and pick it back up
turn around, go forward slightly, stop, and turn back to face the sink
open the bottom drawer, put the soap inside, and close the drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the corner of the bath tub near the sink.
Take the pink soap from the corner of the bath tub.
Turn around and go to the far sink next to the shower.
Put the soap in the sink to the left of the drain. Turn the water of the sink on and then off. Take the soap from the sink.
Go in front of the sink.
Put the soap in the bottom left drawer below the sink counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left, walk towards since, turn right and walk towards bath
Grab the bar of soap off of the bath tub
Turn around, walk towards the sink
Place the soap in the sink, turn the faucet on, then turn it off, grab soap from the sink
Open the cabinet door underneath the sink
Place the bar of soap in the cabinet, then close the door
anns.task_desc: Place the bar of soap in the cabinet underneath the sink
